    <title>Home Page</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../static/home.css">
</head>
<body>
    <nav class="navbar">
        <h1>Welcome to Class Pulse</h1>
    </nav>

    <div class="container">
        <section class="intro">
            <p>ClassPulse is designed to revolutionize the way educational 
               feedback is gathered and analyzed. Its primary purpose is to 
               harness advanced machine learning models to interpret the 
               complex emotions and opinions expressed in student feedback, 
               transforming raw text into actionable insights. In this project, we
               have implemented the above-described system using the four pillars
               of OOD namely Abstraction, Polymorphism, Inheritance, and Encapsulation.</p>
        </section>
        
        <section class="features">
            <h2>Features of Our System:</h2>
            <div class="feature-links">
                <ul>
                    <li tal:condition="user_role in ['TA', 'Student']"><a href="/givefeedback">Give Feedback</a></li>
                    <li tal:condition="user_role in ['Instructor','Teacher']"><a href="/viewfeedback">View Feedback</a></li>
                    <li><a href="/register">User Register</a></li>
                    <li><a href="/login">User Login</a></li>
                    <li><a href="/registercourse">Register Course</a></li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </section>
    </div>
